PRIVACY POLICY

Video Compressor

Last updated: June 1, 2026

This Privacy Policy describes how the Video Compressor mobile application
("the App", "we", "us", or "our") handles information. We are committed to
protecting your privacy. The short version: the App does all of its work on
your device, and we do not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal
data.

1. INFORMATION WE COLLECT

We do not collect any personal information.

The App does not require you to create an account, sign in, or provide any
personal details. We do not collect names, email addresses, phone numbers,
location data, contacts, or any device identifiers.

2. HOW THE APP WORKS (ON-DEVICE PROCESSING)

All video compression, resizing, and related processing happens entirely on
your device. Your videos are never uploaded to any server, cloud service, or
third party. We never see, access, or store your videos. The App can function
completely offline and does not require an internet connection to compress
your videos.

3. PERMISSIONS WE USE

To provide its core feature, the App requests access to the videos and media
on your device:

- Photos and videos / media access (e.g., READ_MEDIA_VIDEO, or storage access
  on older Android versions): This is used solely to let you select a video to
  compress and to save the compressed result back to your device. This access
  is used only while you are using the App and only for the function you
  request. The App does not scan, copy, upload, or transmit your media for any
  other purpose.

You can grant or revoke these permissions at any time in your device's system
settings.

3. FILES YOU CREATE

Compressed videos you create are saved to your device's local storage or photo
gallery, at your direction. These files remain on your device and under your
control. We do not have access to them.

4. THIRD-PARTY SERVICES

The App does not include third-party advertising networks, analytics services,
trackers, or social media SDKs. We do not share any data with third parties,
because we do not collect any data.

5. DATA SHARING AND SALE

We do not sell, rent, trade, or share your personal data with anyone. We have
no personal data to share.

6. DATA SECURITY

Because all processing is performed locally on your device and no data is
transmitted to us, your information stays with you. We recommend keeping your
device secured (for example, with a screen lock) to protect the files stored
on it.

7. CHILDREN'S PRIVACY

The App does not collect any personal information from anyone, including
children under the age of 13. The App is safe for general audiences.

8. CHANGES TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted
on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. We encourage you to review
this policy periodically.



By using the App, you agree to this Privacy Policy.
